<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Welcome to Superfan</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rubik:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f5; font-family: 'Rubik', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: #111111;">
   <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 20px;">
        <div style="max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px #000000; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background-color: #ffffff;">
          <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
          <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 10px ; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ddd2;">
              <img
                                           src="https://cloudflare-b2.shrtchz.workers.dev/image3.png"

                      alt="Superfan"
                      width="150"
                      style="display:block; margin:0; max-width:150px; height:auto; border: 0;"
                    />
              <h1 style="margin: 0; font-family: 'Rubik', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 700; color: #000000;">Welcome to Superfan</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px 18px 18px;">
              <div style="font-family: 'Rubik', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 700; color: #000000; margin: 0 0 10px;">
                {{firstName}}, you made it!
              </div>
              <div style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; color: #000000; margin: 0 0 14px;">
                Your Superfan account is live and your first challenge is waiting. Get ready to acquire african indigenous knowledge through quizzes, streaks, and friendly battles — one question at a time.
              </div>
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border: 1px solid #d8cdbf; margin: 0 0 18px;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding: 14px 12px 12px;">
                    <div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1; color: #111111; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                      You're Officially A Superfan 🚀
                    </div>
                    <div style="font-family: 'Rubik', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 700; color: #000000; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                      Learn smarter. Play harder. Level up.
                    </div>
                    <div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.45; color: #000000;">
                      Superfan turns knowledge acquisition and learning into a game — earn points, beat your streak, and rise up the leaderboard with every quiz you complete.
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 18px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 0 0 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ddd2;">
                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td width="28" valign="top" style="padding-right: 8px;">
                          <table width="20" height="20" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#000000;border-radius: 4px;">
                            <tr>
                              <td align="center" valign="middle">
                                <img src="https://cloudflare-b2.shrtchz.workers.dev/boltz.png" width="11" height="11" style="display:block; border:0;" />
                              </td>
                            </tr>
                          </table>
                        </td>
                        <td style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.35; color: #000000;">
                          <strong>Quiz-first learning</strong> — Every lesson starts with a challenge. Answer questions, get instant feedback, and actually retain what you learn.
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ddd2;">
                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td width="28" valign="top" style="padding-right: 8px;">
                          <table width="20" height="20" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#000000;border-radius: 4px;">
                            <tr>
                              <td align="center" valign="middle">
                                <img src="https://cloudflare-b2.shrtchz.workers.dev/star.png" width="11" height="11" style="display:block; border:0;" />
                              </td>
                            </tr>
                          </table>
                        </td>
                        <td style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.35; color: #000000;">
                          <strong>Streaks &amp; rewards</strong> — Show up every day, keep your streak alive, and unlock badges as your language skills grow.
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 10px 0 0;">
                    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td width="28" valign="top" style="padding-right: 8px;">
                          <table width="20" height="20" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#000000;border-radius: 4px;">
                            <tr>
                              <td align="center" valign="middle">
                                <img src="https://cloudflare-b2.shrtchz.workers.dev/board.png" width="11" height="11" style="display:block; border:0;" />
                              </td>
                            </tr>
                          </table>
                         
                        </td>
                        <td style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.35; color: #000000;">
                          <strong>Compete &amp; climb</strong> — Challenge friends, climb the weekly leaderboard, and prove your language skills under pressure.
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <div align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0 0 16px;">
                <a href="{{start_quiz_url}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #000000; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1; font-weight: 700; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 999px;">
                  Start Your First Quiz
                </a>
              </div>
              <div style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.45; color: #000000; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                Didn't sign up for Superfan NG? You can safely ignore this email — nothing will change.
              </div>
              <div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.45; color: #000000; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                Need help or have questions? Shoot us an email at 
                <span style="color:#000000; text-decoration:none; pointer-events:none; cursor:default;">
                  superfanng@superfan.ng
                </span>
              </div>
    
              <div align="center" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <div style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; color: #000000;">With love,</div>
                <div style="font-family: 'Rubik', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 700; color: #000000;">
                  The Superfan NG Team <img src="https://cloudflare-b2.shrtchz.workers.dev/love.png" alt="love" width="11" height="11" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; border: 0;" />
                
                </div>
              </div>
              <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e8ddd2; margin: 0 0 10px;" />

              <div align="center" style="text-align: center; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4; color: #9ca3af; margin-bottom: 3px;">
                © 2026 Superfan NG. All rights reserved.
              </div>
              <div align="center" style="text-align: center; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4; color: #9ca3af;">
                You're receiving this email because you signed up for a Superfan account.
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        </div>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>